name: ResNeXt50_32x4d for Image Classification
full_description: ResNeXt50_32x4d is a variant of the ResNet architecture that incorporates group convolutions, enhancing both efficiency and performance. Designed for image classification tasks, ResNeXt50_32x4d offers a balance between model complexity and accuracy, making it suitable for a wide range of computer vision applications.
keywords: image classification, deep learning, ResNeXt50_32x4d, residual networks, group convolutions, computer vision
author: Frank Wilson

ai_model.name: ResNeXt50_32x4d
ai_model.description: A convolutional neural network model with group convolutions designed for efficient and high-accuracy image classification.
